{"tid":703140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【熱烈地】美國宣布對中國500億美元商品加徵關稅　首批7月6日實施","createTime":"2018-06-15T13:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T17:44:10.000Z","uid":147314,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"4fce59bb1111c96cb1fe3af9330e68b95c2b3e9a","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:12:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2096163/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2096163%2F&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZicVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=df0402cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2096163/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國宣布對中國500億美元商品加徵關稅 首批7月6日實施</strong><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰火重燃，美國公布對500億美元中國進口商品加徵25%關稅的清單，清單包括1102種產品，包括「中國製造2025」計劃中的產品。首批340億美元中國進口產品，將於7月6日加徵關稅。"},{"pid":"815c7328ea169abba27a905984d0e5423cc290ac","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>特朗普：若中國報復 將追加關稅</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，如果中國報復，美國將追加更多關稅，「美國不能再容忍通過不公平的經濟做法損失我們的技術和知識產權」。<br />\n<br />\n對中國產品加徵關稅，是美國今年稍早進行301調查後採取的行動。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤表示，為應對中國盜用美國的知識產權、強制轉讓美國技術、網絡攻擊等威脅，必須採取強而有力的防禦行動，來保護美國在技術和創新方面的領先地位。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，中國政府正在通過不公平貿易和「中國製造2025」等產業政策，破壞美國的高科技產業和經濟領導力，而技術和創新是美國最大的經濟資產，特朗普意識到，必須立即採取立場來維護公平貿易，保護美國的競爭力。"},{"pid":"c4c564d90352f308c35bc916fd2aaf748f0af54c","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:13:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>萊特希澤：針對「中國製造2025」 保護美國競爭力</strong><br />\n<br />\n清單主要針對「中國製造2025」產業政策相關產品，包括航空航天，信息和通信技術，機器人，工業機械，新材料和汽車等行業。但不包括美國消費者通常購買的商品，如手機或電視機。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室表示，清單包含兩組，第一組涵蓋340億美元中國進口產品，涉及商品項目由4月初公布初始清單的約1300項，減至818項，相關關稅將於7月6日徵收。<br />\n<br />\n而第二組的284個項目，涉及160億美元中國進口產品，均是受惠於「中國製造2025」政策，須要再經過公開諮詢及聽證會，才能有最終拍板。"},{"pid":"ec79abbb68b8816383e856f190df50737d3a7ce5","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2096169/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2096169%2F&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZicVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f6b9ed60\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2096169/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國商務部：將立即對等反擊美國加徵關稅</strong><br />\n<br />\n中美打響貿易戰，美國正式宣布分階段對500億美元中國進口商品加徵25%關稅，中國商務部回應稱，將立即出台同等規模、同等力度的徵稅措施，雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果將同時失效。<br />\n<br />\n中國早前已擬定對約500億美元的美國進口商品加徵25%關稅，涉及<span style=\"color: red;\">飛機、大豆</span>等。"},{"pid":"b0f3dc8bc76179ded7505d9863140e9f11a686e0","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>反對美方損人不利己 此前談判成果將失效</strong><br />\n<br />\n中國商務部發言人表示，中美雙方曾就經貿問題開展多輪磋商，力圖解決分歧，實現雙贏。但美方置雙方已經形成的共識於不顧，反覆無常，挑起貿易戰，令人深感遺憾。他稱，美方此舉既損害雙邊利益，也破壞世界貿易秩序，中方堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，中方不想打貿易戰，但面對「美方損人不利已的短視行為」，中方不得不強而有力回擊，堅決捍衛國家和人民利益、經濟全球化和多邊貿易體制。中方將立即出台同等規模、同等力度的徵稅措施，雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果將同時失效。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，當今時代發起貿易戰不符合全球利益，呼籲各國採取共同行動，制止這種過時和倒退的行為，捍衛人類共同利益。"},{"pid":"b2e5e8271d97f39d0258d19560109c62e78ed2b7","tid":703140,"uid":78143,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F152731_22f88faada771373a07c0289ca8bbe7a.gif&h=197902a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c77196488e704e92a6223ded9c80adde592c564","tid":703140,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"股joy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6af790557e0b0ea6e7fb37c49daace10073f1e7","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"各位黎個小慶祝先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cd735a9f7efcb86244268a94f2affb6975870d","tid":703140,"uid":6604,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"天佑美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacb1be9e2c2b1676e61f69f1a1f8daffc52fd70","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:23:45.000Z","msg":"王毅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9eb8c2e41d3e61082d96fd7f5fc4e8d1263d14e","tid":703140,"uid":82033,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"減入口，推內銷<br />\n點樣損人不利己？<br />\n<br />\n有總你支那照跟丫"},{"pid":"47deb67c9ed69f1258b9ea1d9a40887e15cf43b7","tid":703140,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"可以亮劍未"},{"pid":"a5400c4a7879746ee1e2d37608fcc1914c938c50","tid":703140,"uid":54264,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:28:34.000Z","msg":"侵侵真係冇路捉"},{"pid":"4a73b1cd356409c0356931aa1a3798cf89a3027e","tid":703140,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"809a33ee34d607da319a91aac1c393c1681a8767","tid":703140,"uid":141151,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"4a73b1cd356409c0356931aa1a3798cf89a3027e","tid":703140,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:32:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"呢度邊到有人驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095033e4c246e362dca8a222cffd86761a10b074","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:39:37.000Z","msg":"接住黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806150264-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201806150264-1.aspx&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZicVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a4a48c17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201806150264-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳美對中擬第2份關稅清單 鎖定1000億美元商品</strong><br />\n<br />\n（中央社北京／華盛頓15日綜合外電報導）正當美國準備在今天對價值500億美元進口中國貨品宣布加徵關稅清單的同時，美方據悉即將擬訂完成第2份關稅清單，鎖定價值1000億美元的中國貨品。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普正準備對中國進口貨品頒行第一輪關稅措施，預料將引發北京以牙還牙方式回應。一名美國官員告訴路透社，這第2份清單是川普貫徹「相當重大」關稅行動的決定之一。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉川普政府關稅計畫思維的3名知情人士對路透社表示，如同首份500億美元關稅清單，這份1000億美元關稅清單也將經歷相同公聽程序，意味至少須費時60天才能生效。"},{"pid":"a493469a70e9720e869bc27e8f2b96bdc98861df","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"為了盡可能減少美國消費者和企業受到的衝擊，第2份關稅清單特別挑選能從其他國家獲得充分替代供應的貨品。但要免除任何衝擊，恐怕不可能。<br />\n<br />\n一名聽過美國商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）簡報的人士表示：「要鎖定價值1000億美元的中國進口品，就會觸及消費品，這是一定的。」<br />\n<br />\n這名人士還說，羅斯表示，這份清單鎖定中國進口占比不超過33%的貨品種類，讓美方較容易轉往其他國家尋求貨源。"},{"pid":"1e6876c1593d5f98623e1ae0328880a92f1f59c5","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"路透社分析美國人口調查與統計局（U.S. Census Bureau）公布的4月進口數據，發現在中國進口占比不高於40%的貨品種類中，共有7600項來自中國的消費品和工業產品還能加徵關稅，這些貨品合計價值1010億美元。<br />\n<br />\n另一名熟悉美國政府思維的人士表示，以33%的進口占比作為門檻，恐怕難以達到1000億美元的規模。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部和美國貿易代表署的新聞官員，拒絕談論關稅清單計畫。（譯者：張正芊/核稿：張佑之）1070615"},{"pid":"73c40f73a29948ab5f92814beb9138092c927374","tid":703140,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"把劍再唔亮就生銹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85a6394dc1df01c91902c8222c7372c1bc0a07c","tid":703140,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd8e6fe1c8aa88158e16f061c5aa6ca450028ac6","tid":703140,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"美國賤種冇資格用偉大我國製造產品<br />\n中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f4e56a82afd786bb91dceff8e96bb24326dff8","tid":703140,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔係立即實施，即係有空間講數，即係可能又傾掂數，即係好消息。股樓gogogo"},{"pid":"173b6773cc80c785e837787720380afae55887b1","tid":703140,"uid":162272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"等睇攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393060eb78ba8b8ba3537d9612fd3d27921a0a13","tid":703140,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:12:24.000Z","msg":"亮劍啦 亮左去邊呀？"},{"pid":"82d008c377bcc193be01a03c2d824feebe617ce3","tid":703140,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f4e56a82afd786bb91dceff8e96bb24326dff8","tid":703140,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔係立即實施，即係有空間講數，即係可能又傾掂數，即係好消息。股樓gogogo"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:13:31.000Z","msg":"340億喺7月6日實施<br />\n其餘要過public hearing"},{"pid":"cf98a9554f38916c38cb38b03bc6a01b72f82c73","tid":703140,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"This list of products consists of two sets of U.S tariff lines.  The first set contains 818 lines of the original 1,333 lines that were included on the proposed list published on April 6.  These lines cover approximately $34 billion worth of imports from China.  USTR has determined to impose an additional duty of 25 percent on these 818 product lines after having sought and received views from the public and advice from the appropriate trade advisory committees.  Customs and Border Protection will begin to collect the additional duties on July 6, 2018.<br />\n<br />\nThe second set contains 284 proposed tariff lines identified by the interagency Section 301 Committee as benefiting from Chinese industrial policies, including the &ldquo;Made in China 2025&rdquo; industrial policy.  These 284 lines, which cover approximately $16 billion worth of imports from China, will undergo further review in a public notice and comment process, including a public hearing.  After completion of this process, USTR will issue a final determination on the products from this list that would be subject to the additional duties.<br />\n<br />\nUSTR recognizes that some U.S. companies may have an interest in importing items from China that are covered by the additional duties. Accordingly, USTR will soon provide an opportunity for the public to request the exclusion of particular products from the additional duties subject to this action.  USTR will issue a notice in the Federal Register with details regarding this process within the next few weeks.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/june/ustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fustr.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fpolicy-offices%2Fpress-office%2Fpress-releases%2F2018%2Fjune%2Fustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZicVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cb8f918d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/june/ustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products</a>"},{"pid":"6aff1555dba83d384889a4eeafd815dc0e896a89","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672926872085674672ccfae87d50a27fe7dd9546","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa41dd9e220574092158f6131332f04837a373f","tid":703140,"uid":1723,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"侵：習大大生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe33c13a3e69d897ee7fa45748bed156e012d42d","tid":703140,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4eac240820cfce88d18912d5a6d3274a52bfa53","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe33c13a3e69d897ee7fa45748bed156e012d42d","tid":703140,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"cheers <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b415a6363052afafe4fa0fa329ee4486527cbbd","tid":703140,"uid":28624,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T14:37:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩贏左第二場質易戰咁快又再開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估到美國會繼續咬死支那唔放<br />\n<br />\n果班話美國放生中興<br />\n侵支持者俾侵撚狗既死哂去邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd1d843283cabb06e29dc1fbdce5dc53a3337b6","tid"