Tax"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"TheftTax"},{"pid":"7b86d8cb897cbcc6e82748168c43f5a8c8d580bc","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1867849/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1867849%2F&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZicVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=094c3996\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1867849/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部：中美所有經貿成果將失效<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/06/15/1867849_945e255535ba142811cd86833a13c287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F1867849_945e255535ba142811cd86833a13c287.jpg&h=8a2ca0d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦公室稍早公布對中國輸美產品加徵關稅清單。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷表示，中美雙方曾就經貿問題開展多輪磋商，力圖解決分歧，實現雙贏，惟美方置雙方已經形成的共識於不顧，反復無常，挑起貿易戰。此舉既損害雙邊利益，又破壞世界貿易秩序，中方對此堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，中方並不想打貿易戰，但面對美方損人不利己的短視行為，中方不得不予以強有力回擊，堅決捍衞國家利益和人民利益，堅決捍衞經濟全球化和多邊貿易體制。中方將立即出台同等規模、同等力度的徵稅措施，雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果將同時失效。"},{"pid":"4bf9c2589981d3e40152552970d2b0e7a23654ac","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"失效？<br />\n無用既成果，who fucking care ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4519f9bef7c9b37c6c0c23b0157ed584a339a21","tid":703140,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bba53cbf7ec3450ed62213cadfdb81c7fccfa0","tid":703140,"uid":110124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"留名等美國宣布經濟資助北韓發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad3b74204a422de13200bb77dca5b11e4a0