,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"Trump: 下輪大多佢1000億先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b72fcdfc72056568cb16df65489f6e036ba85f","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c9461ac2afa01d8e543ed3609394d106da8f9a","tid":703140,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b0f3dc8bc76179ded7505d9863140e9f11a686e0","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>反對美方損人不利己 此前談判成果將失效</strong><br />\n<br />\n中國商務部發言人表示，中美雙方曾就經貿問題開展多輪磋商，力圖解決分歧，實現雙贏。但美方置雙方已經形成的共識於不顧，反覆無常，挑起貿易戰，令人深感遺憾。他稱，美方此舉既損害雙邊利益，也破壞世界貿易秩序，中方堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，中方不想打貿易戰，但面對「美方損人不利已的短視行為」，中方不得不強而有力回擊，堅決捍衛國家和人民利益、經濟全球化和多邊貿易體制。中方將立即出台同等規模、同等力度的徵稅措施，雙方此前磋商達成的所有經貿成果將同時失效。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，當今時代發起貿易戰不符合全球利益，呼籲各國採取共同行動，制止這種過時和倒退的行為，捍衛人類共同利益。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:22:05.000Z","msg":"悍衛人類其同利益就係中共解體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:17:05.000Z","msg":"之前乜嘢成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee1dddd58a3ef4979566aaa4f78b2bfde30f805","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"854fbd435be59ae972af2e847b286da7d8fdaf08","tid":703140,"uid":122377,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"其實侵好撚勁 <br />\n由當初美國本地好多人屌佢搞事 打貿易戰會倆敗俱傷 <br />\n到今時今日 全世界都眾志成城支持佢打鳩中國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c193a8ed5c9883da6adc9c58b21f554361270e1","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1fdfea9e7db2ccd7089a1160255350f26333ead","tid":703140,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:35:43.000Z","msg":"Rubio:<br />\nThis is an EXCELLENT move by @realDonaldTrump most of these technology products from #China are made from technology stolen from U.S. companies. They steal over $300 billion worth of technology a year. So these aren&rsquo;t tariffs they are a #TheftTax"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae8b38687844cad433df7debbd6c2f8136c7f86","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf9c2589981d3e40152552970d2b0e7a23654ac","tid":703140,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"失效？<br />\n無用既成果，who fucking care ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7f96ecb684427db4cf075d6ea365208a4e43fb3","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6bba53cbf7ec3450ed62213cadfdb81c7fccfa0","tid":703140,"uid":110124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"留名等美國宣布經濟資助北韓發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:20:16.000Z","msg":"Nike先去起十間廠，支那0間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf3f9c0160bb99b760a8b85b023bfdd1c3d39d7","tid":703140,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad3b74204a422de13200bb77dca5b11e4a090d0","tid":703140,"uid":187839,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"支持支持,你班大陸狗都蝦得我地D香港人耐啦,而家惡人自有惡人治,望都望呢個終國快D死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aea9f15355aeaf07e8604e53e21191c55f7873","tid":703140,"uid":181727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a